{{multiple issues| {{refimprove|date=July 2014}} {{Cleanup|date=June 2014|reason="copy edit"}} {{Orphan|date=July 2014}} }}
'''2010 ISSA Basketball Tournament''' was the [[basketball]] tournament of the [[Iloilo Schools Sports Association]] in 2007.<ref>[http://www.dslondon.org.uk/ISSA-Sports-eng ''ISSA Tournaments'']</ref> Six (6) schools in group A and five (5) schools in group B of the high school division were participating and the tournament was hosted by the [[Central Philippine University]]. Games were held at the De Paul College gym, CPU gym and Iloilo Sports Complex Basketball center. The tournament was held from August 10 through September 14 or 17th, 2007.{{citation needed|date=June 2014}} The champion of group B will go up to group A for the next tournament, while the last place team in group A will be relegated to group B.
