The '''2011 [[Malaysia Open (badminton)|Malaysia Super Series]]''' was the first tournament of the [[2011 BWF Super Series]] in [[badminton]]. It was held in [[Kuala Lumpur]], [[Malaysia]] from 18 January to 23 January 2011.<ref>[http://www.bwfbadminton.org/tournamentcalendar_event.aspx?id=10469&calendarid=103 Malaysia Super Series 2011]</ref>
