{{Infobox Pro hockey team | current = | text_color = blue | bg_color = yellow | team = HC Prešov Penguins | logo = | logosize = 200px | city = [[Prešov]], [[Slovakia]] | league = [[Slovak 1.Liga|1.Liga]] | conference = | division = | founded = {{Start date|1928}} | operated = | arena = '''[[Ice Arena]]''' (Capacity 6.000) | colors = {{Color box|yellow|border=darkgray}} {{Color box|blue|border=darkgray}} {{Color box|black|border=darkgray}} | colours = | owner = | GM = {{flagicon|Slovakia}} František Pulščak | coach = {{flagicon|Slovakia}} Anton Tomko | captain = | media = | affiliates = | website = [http://www.hcpresovpenguins.sk] <!---Franchise history---> | name1 = '''ČSSZ Prešov''' | dates1 = 1953 | name2 = '''Tatran Prešov''' | dates2 = 1964 | name3 = '''VTJ Dukla Prešov''' | dates3 = 1968 | name4 = '''ZPA Prešov''' | dates4 = 1970 | name5 = '''Dragon Prešov''' | dates5 = 1994 | name6 = '''HK VTJ Prešov''' | dates6 = 1997 | name7 = '''HK VTJ Farmakol Prešov''' | dates7 = 1998 | name8 = '''PHK Prešov''' | dates8 = 2003 | name9 = '''HK Lietajúce kone Prešov''' | dates9 = 2005 | name10 = '''HC Prešov 07''' | dates10 = 2008-2015 | name11 = '''HC Prešov Penguins''' | dates11 = 2015-present }} '''HC Prešov Penguins''' is an [[ice hockey]] team playing in the [[Slovak 1.Liga|1.Liga]], the second level of Slovak ice hockey, and were formed in 1928. They play in the city of [[Prešov]], [[Slovakia]] at Ice Arena.
==History== The club was founded in 1928 as '''Snaha Presov'''. They changed their name many times since:
