'''Real Kakamora FC''' is a [[Solomon Islands]] [[Association football|football]] club, which plays in the [[Solomon Islands National Club Championship|Telekom S-League]].

They were last minute replacements for [[Makuru FC]] to join the newly formed league in 2011.<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tabless/solom2011.html#ko Solomon Islands 2011] – RSSSF</ref>

